column5: AHH!
column11: Ah!

column4:
ナイトシェイド！
まだあきらめてなかったんだ！
column5: Nightshade! They haven't given up yet!
column11: Nightshade! They haven't given up yet!

column5: Please protect the village!...
column11: Protect the village...

column5: Please protect this shrine!!
column11: Please protect this shrine!!

column5: Huh!?
column11: Huuh!?

column4: ここを守って欲しいの！
column5: I want you to protect the shrine!
column11: I want you to protect the shrine!

column4:
もし、ここが壊れたら、
住むところがなくなっちゃうし。
column5: If it gets destroyed, I'll have nowhere to live.
column11: If it gets destroyed, I'll have nowhere to live.

column4:
私みたいな、レディーが
野宿なんてことになったら、
悲惨じゃない。
column5: It'd just be too pitiful for a proper lady like me to end up sleeping on the streets!
column11: If a lady like me ends up ends up sleeping on the streets, it'd just be too pitiful.

column5: Please help!
column11: Please help!

column5: Um...Hiya~!
column11: Um, hiya~

column5: I'm talking to you~!
column11: I'm talking to you~

column5: Hm?
column11: Hm?

column4:
私、カオル。
忍びの里の下忍よ。
column5: I'm Kaoru, a Genin here at the Shinobi Village.
column11: I'm Kaoru. A Genin here at the Shinobi Village.

column4: 里を守ってくれて、感謝です。
column5: We owe you a great debt for protecting the village.
column11: We owe you a great debt for protecting the village.

column4:
一時は、どうなることかと
思ったけど。
column5: I had no idea what was going to happen back then.
column11: Before, I had no idea what was going to happen.

column4:
あなたたちのおかげで
助かったよ〜。
column5: But thanks to your help, we were saved~!
column11: But thanks to your help, we were saved~

column5: Don't mention it.
column11: Don't mention it.

column4:
私、貧乏だから〜、
お礼なんてできないんだけど。
せめて、家に寄っていってよ。
column5: We don't have a lot of money, so I can't thank you properly, but won't you please stop by my house?
column11: We don't have a lot of money, so I can't thank you properly, but please, won't you stop by my house?

column4:
お茶とお菓子ぐらいなら
出せるからさ〜。
column5: I can offer you some tea and sweets, at least~!
column11: I can offer you some tea and sweets at least~

column12: // oops! this line is attributed to kay, but his portrait isn't actually on the screen at this point, so it just gets skipped over in-game.

column4:
ここが私の家なんだ〜。
神社なんだけどね。
column5:
This is my house~!
Well, actually, it's a shrine.
column11:
This is my house~
Well, it's really a shrine.

column4:
へぇぇ。
神社に住んでるんだ？
column5: Wow. You really live in a shrine?
column11: Wow. You really live in a shrine?

column4:
本当の家があったんだけど。
戦いでつぶれちゃった。
column5: I used to have a proper house, but it got knocked down during a battle.
column11: I used to have a proper house, but it was destroyed during a battle.

column4:
たぶん、ナイトシェイドが
壊したんだと思うけど。
column5: I think it was most likely Nightshade that destroyed it.
column11: I think it was most likely Nightshade who ruined it.

column4:
もしかして、あなたたち、
記憶にないかな〜。
column5: You don't happen to remember something like that, do you?
column11: You don't happen to remember something like that, do you?

column4:
人形で
私の家を蹴り飛ばしたり、
してないよね〜？
column5: You wouldn't have kicked down my house with a Puppet, right~?
column11: You didn't kick down my house with a mech, right~?

column5: Ah, uh...
column11: Ah, uh...

column5: Probably not.
column11: Probably not.

column4:
だから、今は
神社に泊めてもらってるんだ〜。
column5: Well, that's why I'm staying at a shrine right now~.
column11: Well, that's why I'm staying at a shrine right now~

column5: I-I see...
column11: I-I see...
